Idea : Just sort the given nums array in descending order. It will make the array {1, 0, 0} and will consider all the subsets containing zeros.
Another way : 
   if (i == 0){
      if (sum == 0 && arr[0] = 0) return 2;
      if (sum == 0 || arr[0] == sum) return 1;
      return 0;
  }
